    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Classify a Instagram post for an automation-focused audience . Return only relevant/non_relevant  classification.\n\n-Relevant if it is some interesting news on AI that came out.\n\n-Not Relevant if it's motivational/personal , non-automation coding ,\ncrypto/politics/finance, or tool discounts etc. or vague hype with no build/impact. \n\n-ALSO THINK CLEARLY AS USER IF IT IS REALLY NICE.\n- THINK THAT YOU ARE FINDING DIAMOND IN BUNCH OF GOLD.\n\n\n",
        "messages": {
          "messageValues": [
            {
              "message": "=You are a strict content classifier for an AI news Instagram page.\n\nYour job is to find \"diamond\" posts — breaking news, drama, and major industry moments worth reposting.\n\nRELEVANT criteria (be very strict, only 20-30% should pass):\n- Breaking AI news (new model releases, major announcements)\n- Industry drama (resignations, lawsuits, controversies, boycotts)\n- Big funding rounds or acquisitions\n- Government & AI (regulations, bans, military deals)\n- Major company moves (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Meta, Microsoft)\n- Viral AI moments that sparked public debate\n\nNON_RELEVANT (reject these):\n- Generic AI tips and how-to guides\n- Prompt engineering tutorials\n- \"Here are X tools you should use\" posts\n- Motivational or opinion posts with no news value\n- AI art/video showcases with no news angle\n- Weekly roundup posts\n- Posts that just explain a concept\n\nWhen in doubt, mark as non_relevant. Be harsh. You are looking for diamonds."
            },
            {
              "type": "AIMessagePromptTemplate",
              "message": "=-Classify these Instagram posts as relevant or non_relevant.\n\n{{ $json.posts.map((p, i) => '━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n📌 POST ' + (i+1) + '\\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\\n🔗 URL       : ' + (p.url ?? 'N/A') + '\\n❤️ Likes     : ' + (p.likesCount ?? 0) + '\\n💬 Comments  : ' + (p.commentsCount ?? 0) + '\\n🕐 Timestamp : ' + (p.timestamp ?? 'N/A') + '\\n📝 Caption   : ' + (p.caption ?? 'N/A')).join('\\n\\n') }}\n\n\n-Reply ONLY with a valid JSON array, no markdown, no bold, no explanation:\n[{\"url\":\"...\",\"classification\":\"relevant\"},{\"url\":\"...\",\"classification\":\"non_relevant\"}]"
            }
          ]
        },
        "batching": {}
      },
